
#require no-eden


  $ eagerepo
  $ enable rebase
  $ setconfig experimental.evolution.allowdivergence=1

  $ newrepo repo
  $ drawdag <<'EOS'
  >    D    # D is orphaned.
  >    |
  > C2 C C1 # amend: C -> C1 -> C2
  >   \|/
  >    B Z
  >    |/
  >    A
  > EOS

  $ cp -R ../repo ../repob

C -> C2 relation is copied with singletransaction.

